&lt;td width=&quot;555&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep Understanding of the Financial Services legal and regulatory framework and the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;ethical principles underpinning them. Thorough understanding of new or changing&amp;nbsp;legislation and legal practice on the insurance sector. Understanding of the impact of&amp;nbsp;exposure to risk and strategies to manage, mitigate and transfer risk.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
