&lt;p&gt;Clients and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;Colleagues&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;555&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep understanding of&amp;nbsp; the principles of how to build strong internal and external&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;relationships. Able to demonstrate an in depth understanding of customer service&amp;nbsp;standards and the culture of the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
