&lt;td width=&quot;151&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Processes and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;Procedures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;555&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep understanding of the processes and procedures within own role and how these&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;are impacted by insurance market practices and agreements. Able to evaluate how&amp;nbsp;these support the delivery of the operational and strategic objectives of the business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
