&lt;td width=&quot;555&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep understanding of how the insurance market may be affected by external&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;change. Understanding of how to assess the impact of competitor strategy on&amp;nbsp;businesses and their market position and how to use this knowledge to contribute toorganisational strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
