&lt;td style=&quot;height: 109px;&quot; width=&quot;556&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Applies specialist technical knowledge and experience to unfamiliar and/or complex situations. Proactively responds to insurance market changes to deliver positive outcomes to all stakeholders. Consistent application of legal insurance principles, knowledge of the market structure and its processes and procedures and documentation to a range of complex situations.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
